1
00:01:36,910 --> 00:01:39,240
我像块石头
I am a stone.

2
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:43,510
纹丝不动
I do not move.

3
00:01:48,190 --> 00:01:53,650
我慢慢地把雪放进嘴里
Very slowly, I put snow in my mouth,

4
00:01:53,790 --> 00:01:56,890
这样 狼就看不见我的呼气
then he won't see my breath.

5
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:08,670
我耐心等待 等它再靠近些
I take my time. I let him come closer.

6
00:02:08,810 --> 00:02:11,570
我只有一发子弹
I have only one bullet.

7
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:13,480
我瞄准狼的眼睛
I aim at his eye.

8
00:02:13,610 --> 00:02:18,950
手指放在扳掣上
Very gently,my finger presses on the trigger.

9
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:25,020
我不发抖
I do not tremble.

10
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:28,960
也不害怕
I have no fear.

11
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:32,160
我已经是个大孩子了
I'm a big boy now.

12
00:02:36,100 --> 00:02:37,540
准备 瓦希里！
Ready,Vassili?

13
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,830
瓦希里 开枪！
Now,Vassili. Fire!

14
00:02:39,970 --> 00:02:44,950
开枪 瓦希里！
Fire,Vassili! Fire!

15
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:53,540
兵临城下

16
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:46,970
快 快 抓紧时间
Come on,pick your feet up.

17
00:03:47,050 --> 00:03:50,430
起来 起来 准备上车
Get on your feet. Prepare to board the train.

18
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:01,940
现在跟我来 这边 伙计
You there,come along with me now. This way,pal.

19
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:06,620
大家起来
All civilians,get out!

20
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,390
起来 准备上火车 快走
Make way,let the civilians off.

21
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:12,100
这是部队专车
This is a military convoy.

22
00:04:12,230 --> 00:04:17,430
除了英勇的军人 所有人都下车
No one stays on board but our valiant soldiers.

23
00:04:17,570 --> 00:04:20,540
这是护送红军
This is a convoy

24
00:04:20,670 --> 00:04:24,580
前往斯大林格勒的专车
to Stalingrad...

25
00:04:27,180 --> 00:04:35,110
本列车只接载我们的英勇军人
only for the soldiers of the Red Army.

26
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:39,620
这是护送红军
This is a military convoy.

27
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:44,110
前往斯大林格勒的专车
to Stalingrad...

28
00:04:44,110 --> 00:04:47,150
到齐
All aboard!

29
00:05:13,090 --> 00:05:15,190
1942年秋季
Autumn,1942.

30
00:05:15,330 --> 00:05:18,820
纳粹党的军队横行欧洲
Europe lies crushed beneath the Nazi jackboot.

31
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:25,440
德意志第三帝国势头正盛
The German Third Reich I sat the height of its power.

32
00:05:25,940 --> 00:05:28,870
正攻入苏联心脏
Hitler's armies are charging through the heart of the Soviet Union...

33
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:31,070
向中东的油田进发
towards the oilfields of Asia.

34
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:33,770
他们只剩下一道防线
One last obstacle remains.

35
00:05:33,910 --> 00:05:37,310
全球命运全系于… 伏尔加河畔一个城市
A city on the Volga... where the fate of the world is being decided.

36
00:05:37,450 --> 00:05:38,780
斯大林格勒
Stalingrad.

37
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:07,130
所有军队和市民
The Red Army and all citizens of the Soviet Union

38
00:06:07,230 --> 00:06:12,530
势必捍卫苏维埃的每一寸领土 决战到底
must defend every inch of Soviet soil.Must fight to the last.

39
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:16,020
1942年9月20日

40
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:35,210
斯大林同志有令：绝不后退
Glorious comrade Stalin... has ordered not another step backwards.

41
00:06:35,210 --> 00:06:38,870
苏联人民要争取自由
The people of the Soviet Union shall be free.

42
00:06:39,110 --> 00:06:41,440
决不沦为奴隶
Never gonna be a slaves！

43
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:58,290
同志们 前进！
Go forward,comrades.

44
00:06:58,430 --> 00:07:00,530
一步也不能后退
Not a step backwards!

45
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:18,920
这些信是苏联母亲写给
Listen to these letters sent by Russian mothers...

46
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:21,990
在前线的儿子 听听吧
to their sons on the front.

47
00:07:22,690 --> 00:07:25,020
瓦洛亚 我儿…
"Volodya,my child,

48
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:28,180
我知道这是为了祖国
I know that it's for our motherland一

49
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:35,960
我知道你是为国捐躯
"I know that it's for our motherland that you are giving your life.

50
00:07:51,650 --> 00:07:56,610
大家都知道你绝不退缩
"Everyone here knows that you will not fall back.

51
00:07:56,820 --> 00:08:00,320
大家都以你为荣
"Everyone here is proud of you.

52
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:03,730
你父亲死了 兄弟死了
"Your father is dead. Your brothers are dead.

53
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:07,270
你要向法西斯党讨回这份血债
Avenge us on the hordes of fascists. "

54
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,260
趴下！…
Everybody drops here!

55
00:08:15,540 --> 00:08:17,310
找掩护！
Find coverd！

56
00:08:46,310 --> 00:08:48,100
一 不准动 一 留在船上
Nobody move! Stay on the boat!

57
00:08:48,310 --> 00:08:50,510
回来 否则开枪！
Get back or I'll shoot!

58
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:54,880
回来 否则我们就开枪！ 枪毙叛徒！
Back from the rails,or we shoot. Shoot the traitors!

59
00:09:12,470 --> 00:09:15,400
斯大林格勒码头

60
00:09:16,700 --> 00:09:18,570
准备上岸！
Ready ashore!

61
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,590
快 快 走
Come on,come on! Move!

62
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:34,940
快点 同志们
Come on,comrades,

63
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:39,360
快点 同志们
Come on,comrades, come on!

64
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,360
快走 否则会被击中!
Move,or you'll be shot!

65
00:09:57,810 --> 00:09:59,640
这边！分开
Over here,stretcher!

66
00:10:05,690 --> 00:10:08,150
有枪的人就开枪
The one with the rifle shoots!

67
00:10:08,290 --> 00:10:11,090
每两个人一支枪
One out of two gets a rifle.

68
00:10:11,220 --> 00:10:14,090
有枪的人走前 没枪的人随后
The one without follows him!

69
00:10:14,290 --> 00:10:17,730
有枪的人倒下了…
When the one with the rifle gets killed,

70
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:23,288
尾随的人 就检起枪 继续射击
the one who is following picks up the rifle and shoots!

71
00:10:23,290 --> 00:10:28,140
有枪的人就开枪
The one with the rifle shoots!

72
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:31,580
没枪的人随后
The one without follows him!

73
00:10:31,710 --> 00:10:35,110
有枪的人倒下了…
When the one with the rifle gets killed,

74
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:41,280
尾随的人就检起枪 继续射击
the one who is following... picks up the rifle and shoots!

75
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:48,660
有枪的人就开枪 走这边 没枪的人随后
The one with the rifle shoots! This way,now.The one without follows him!

76
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:14,050
伟大的红军士兵
Soldiers of the glorious Red Army,

77
00:11:14,190 --> 00:11:19,830
现在起 我们不成功便成仁
from now on...it is either victory or death!

78
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:23,590
违抗命令者 按军法处置 我需要枪
一 Those who retreat will be shot. 一 I need a rifle.

79
00:11:23,730 --> 00:11:30,970
懦夫和叛徒 坚决就地正法
There will be no mercy For cowards and traitors! Achtung!

80
00:12:48,300 --> 00:12:50,220
Aah!

81
00:13:18,210 --> 00:13:21,340
无望的了 同志们！撤退！
It's hopeless,comrades. Get back!

82
00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:23,750
撤退！…
Pullback!

83
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:29,360
撤退！…
Pullback! Get back! Get back!

84
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,920
奉苏联之名…
In the name of the Soviet Union,

85
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:36,200
你们不准后退 否则被杀！
not a step backwards, or we shoot.

86
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:39,430
不准后退半步！
No retreat! Not a step back!

87
00:13:39,570 --> 00:13:42,560
绝不宽待 逃兵将被击毙!懦夫将被抢毙!
一 No mercy! 一 Deserters will be shot. Cowards will be shot!

88
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:44,290
开枪！
一 Fire! 一 Shoot the traitors!

89
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:49,280
枪毙叛徒！
Cowards will be shot!

90
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:52,670
绝不宽待懦夫！
No mercy for cowards!

91
00:14:29,420 --> 00:14:32,080
俄罗斯人 投降吧！
Russians,surrender.

92
00:14:32,220 --> 00:14:34,080
投降就可以重返家园
You will see your home again.

93
00:14:34,250 --> 00:14:36,880
这场仗不关你们事
This is not your war.

94
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:41,690
加入德军 他们体恤你们的苦况
Join your German comrades, They understand your suffering...

95
00:14:41,830 --> 00:14:45,530
比你们的军官更关心你们
and will care more for you than your own officers,

96
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:48,790
你们的军官只派你们去送死
who are only sending you to your death.

97
00:14:48,940 --> 00:14:51,870
第三帝国不是你们的敌人
The Third Reich Is not your enemy.

98
00:14:52,010 --> 00:14:54,570
你们的敌人是嗜血的斯大林
The enemy is blood thirsty Stalin And his Bolshevik camp,

99
00:14:54,710 --> 00:15:01,310
与他的党徒 他们抢走你们的土地 驱逐你们的父亲
who have stolen your land,who have deported your father一

100
00:15:23,070 --> 00:15:24,040
开火！
Fire!

101
00:15:35,620 --> 00:15:39,520
不容许敌人踏足斯大林格勒

102
00:17:22,320 --> 00:17:27,190
政委同志 这样我们会被发现的
You'll get us caught, comrade Commissar.

103
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:52,080
政委同志 请让我来
With your permission, comrade Commissar.

104
00:18:23,850 --> 00:18:25,750
应该先杀哪一个?
Which one should I aim at first?

105
00:18:25,890 --> 00:18:30,080
应该先等爆炸才开枪
You should wait...till there's an explosion.

106
00:18:41,770 --> 00:18:43,240
你懂开枪吗?
Do you know how to shoot?

107
00:18:44,900 --> 00:18:46,130
一点点
A little.

108
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,520
该死!
Damn!Damn!

109
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:40,290
别开枪 他发现我们了
Don't shoot. Don't shoot. He's looking at us.

110
00:20:45,390 --> 00:20:48,520
谢谢你 政委同志
Thank you, comrade Commissar.

111
00:20:54,530 --> 00:20:59,800
丹尼洛夫 第21步兵团
Danilov,political officer, second class.

112
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:02,130
第二政治委员
Twenty一 first infantry.

113
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:22,850
瓦希里柴瑟夫
"Vassili Zaitsev."

114
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:27,630
1942年9月20日…
"On this day, September the 20th,1942,

115
00:21:27,770 --> 00:21:30,670
一名来自乌拉尔的年轻牧羊人
"a shepherd boy from the Urals...

116
00:21:34,470 --> 00:21:37,970
抵达伏尔加河畔的斯大林格勒
"arrived in the city of Stalingrad, on the banks of the Volga.

117
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:41,250
他名叫瓦希里柴瑟夫
"His name is Vassili Zaitsev.

118
00:21:41,250 --> 00:21:47,000
他是响应斯大林同志的号召而来
"Like thousands before him,he came to answer comrade Stalin's call.

119
00:21:48,620 --> 00:21:50,420
只拿着一支枪…
"Armed with a rifle,

120
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:52,620
就很快令纳粹侵略者意识到…
he quickly made the fascist invader realize that...

121
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:57,590
他们不及早回头
"from now on he would be punished for every step he took in the motherland;

122
00:21:57,960 --> 00:22:02,230
只有死路一条
that from here on, the only way was back."

123
00:22:04,140 --> 00:22:05,830
觉得怎样?
What do you think?

124
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:10,900
我认为政委同志太过奖了
I think comrade Commissar's been overgenerous.

125
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:19,810
1942年9月22日

126
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:33,150
放我过去！ 放我过去！
Let me go! Let me go!

127
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:36,530
不准越线！
Don't cross the line!

128
00:22:36,670 --> 00:22:41,900
斯大林同志有令：民众不得离城
By order of comrade Stalin, no civilian can leave the city.

129
00:22:43,210 --> 00:22:45,200
回去！
Get back!

130
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:46,680
放我过去！
Let me go!

131
00:22:46,810 --> 00:22:50,150
走开 否则我们开枪！
Stand away, or we will open fire.

132
00:22:59,990 --> 00:23:02,370
走开!
Stand away!

133
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,690
走开！
Get back!

134
00:23:05,630 --> 00:23:07,060
回去 否则我们开枪！
Get back or we shoot!

135
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:09,290
走开…
Back! Keep back!

136
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:14,370
给斯大林同志的特使让路
Make way for comrade Stalin 's envoy!

137
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:20,340
我有执行命令
I carried out my orders.

138
00:23:20,610 --> 00:23:23,310
派遣了所有士兵
I sent in all of my boys.

139
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:26,210
不过 敌我军力悬殊
But the Germans engulfed us.

140
00:23:27,250 --> 00:23:31,590
他们有大炮、飞机、坦克…
They have artillery, aircraft,tanks.

141
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,210
我们呢?有什么?
And me,what did I have?

142
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:36,350
死守的神圣任务
The sacred duty to resist!

143
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:38,890
我必须报告最高领袖
I have to report to the boss.

144
00:23:40,930 --> 00:23:44,160
你最好自我了断
Perhaps you'd prefer to avoid the red tape.

145
00:24:07,060 --> 00:24:08,530
我叫…
My name is...

146
00:24:08,730 --> 00:24:14,390
尼吉达.卓基域治.赫鲁晓夫
Nikita Sergeyevich Kruschev.

147
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:18,200
我来接管这里
I've come to take things in hand here.

148
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:22,000
这里不是库斯克
This city is not Kursk...

149
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:25,580
不是基辅 也不是明斯克
nor is it Kiev,nor Minsk.

150
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:29,640
而是斯大林格勒
This city is Stalingrad.

151
00:24:29,780 --> 00:24:32,310
斯大林…格勒
Stalingrad!

152
00:24:33,620 --> 00:24:36,610
本市背负着领袖的名字
This city bears the name of the boss.

153
00:24:36,760 --> 00:24:39,850
不仅是个城市 更是个标志
It's more than a city, it's a symbol.

154
00:24:39,990 --> 00:24:44,990
假如德军占领了这里
If the Germans capture this city,

155
00:24:45,130 --> 00:24:48,500
全国就会瓦解
the entire country will collapse.

156
00:24:49,300 --> 00:24:56,330
现在我希望士兵们昂起头来！
Now,I want our boys... to raise their heads.

157
00:24:56,610 --> 00:25:00,200
我要他们拿出勇气来！
I want them to act like they have balls!

158
00:25:00,350 --> 00:25:05,050
不准他们再怕得屎滚尿流！
I want them to stop shitting their pants!

159
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:11,290
你们是政委
That's your job.

160
00:25:11,290 --> 00:25:17,190
激励士气是你们的职责
As political officers, I'm counting on you.

161
00:25:18,860 --> 00:25:23,820
你 你有什么建议?
You, what's your suggestion?

162
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:29,000
把退缩的将军、参谋长统统枪毙
Shoot all the other generals who have retreated... and their chiefs of staff too.

163
00:25:29,540 --> 00:25:31,810
立下范例
M-Make some examples.

164
00:25:31,940 --> 00:25:35,710
放逐逃兵的家属 做过了
一 D - D - Deport families of the deserters.一 Yeah,that's all been done.

165
00:25:35,850 --> 00:25:37,750
给士兵希望
Give them hope!

166
00:25:50,330 --> 00:25:53,630
他们现在不是死于敌军就是我军
Here,the men's only choice is between German bullets and ours.

167
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:55,890
不过 还有另一条路
But there's another way.

168
00:25:56,040 --> 00:26:00,040
就是勇气之路、爱国之路
The way of courage.The way of love of the motherland.

169
00:26:00,040 --> 00:26:01,770
我们必须再次印发军报
We must publish the army newspaper again.

170
00:26:01,910 --> 00:26:06,280
报导英勇事迹 歌颂报国精神
We must tell magnificent stories. Stories that extol... sacrifice,bravery.

171
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:08,610
确立必胜信念
We must make them believe in the victory.

172
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:13,380
燃点群众的希望 激发斗志
We must give them hope, pride,a desire to fight.

173
00:26:13,690 --> 00:26:17,120
是的 我们要立下范例
Yes,we need to make examples.

174
00:26:17,260 --> 00:26:19,590
但那是供人学习的范例
But examples to follow.

175
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:21,550
我们需要…
What we need...

176
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:24,820
英雄
are heroes.

177
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:31,100
这里有英雄?
Do you know any heroes around here?

178
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:35,470
有 同志 我认识一个
Yes,comrade, I know one.

179
00:26:41,110 --> 00:26:42,580
那是我！
That's me!

180
00:26:42,980 --> 00:26:46,420
瓦希里！那是我！
"Vassili Zaitsev." That's me!

181
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,420
你没做梦
No,you're not dreaming.

182
00:26:48,550 --> 00:26:50,220
的确是你的名字！
It's your name.

183
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:52,690
我们的文章上了头版！
We made the front page.

184
