“称赞”怎样串?  PRAISE
一 Praise?  - R - A - I - S - E.

262
00:31:29,810 --> 00:31:35,070
还有 希望我能不负所望
And... I hope that I can live up...

263
00:31:35,070 --> 00:31:43,580
不负所望…
to your expectations. - A - T - I - O - N - S. Expectations.

264
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:46,350
